By Itamar Kasztelanski He is one of the best protected head of states in the world.After the 1995 assassination of Prime Minister Rabin by a Israeli Jew , the protection protocols were updated and changed and they are reviewed all the time.He has heavily protected limo and his security personnel are one of the best trained and equipped. Only few days back the Israel press noted a new weapon held by a member of the security detail, an Anti-Drone Gun. This is Prime Minister Netanyahu on a tour in Israel. Source: Quora